  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Classic puzzle games recreated in VR</h2><br>Did you ever play with little cubes with balls inside it?<br>Just roll the balls to where they belong. Seems easy, but it's not!<br><br>Carefully designed to bring back classic puzzles to VR.<br><br>There are even more fun and interesting puzzles that was designed from scratch.<br>New puzzles have moving parts that was not possible in physical form.<br>More puzzles will be added.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Supported VR</h2>It currently supports HTC Vive . Oculus Touch support planned.",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Classic puzzle games recreated in VR</h2><br>Did you ever play with little cubes with balls inside it?<br>Just roll the balls to where they belong. Seems easy, but it's not!<br><br>Carefully designed to bring back classic puzzles to VR.<br><br>There are even more fun and interesting puzzles that was designed from scratch.<br>New puzzles have moving parts that was not possible in physical form.<br>More puzzles will be added.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Supported VR</h2>It currently supports HTC Vive . Oculus Touch support planned.",
